metadata.editComments:
I don't think there's a proper way to title this one, due to the van Buuren vs. deadmau5' controversy:

"Let Them Know" was supposed to be released as a collab by both, even been featured in van Buuren's ASOT #585, but deadmau5 ended cancelling it, because he didn't like how it turned out.

He then released it as "Notos" in his Splice pack "Chimaera". Personally liked the energy a lot.
